<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Payment Request Created - Origin Food House</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="margin: 0;">Payment Request Created</h1>
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 30px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
    <p>Hi {{ownerName}},</p>

    <p>Your payment request for <strong>{{storeName}}</strong> has been created successfully.</p>

    <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Payment Details:</h3>
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Tier:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{requestedTier}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Amount:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">${{amount}} USD</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Billing Cycle:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">Annual</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Reference Number:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-family: monospace; color: #4CAF50;"><strong>{{referenceNumber}}</strong></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #856404;">Bank Transfer Instructions:</h3>
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Bank Name:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{bankName}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Account Name:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{accountName}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Account Number:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-family: monospace;">{{accountNumber}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Reference:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-family: monospace; color: #d32f2f;"><strong>{{referenceNumber}}</strong></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 15px; font-size: 14px; color: #856404;">
        <strong>Important:</strong> Please include the reference number in your transfer to ensure fast processing.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>Complete the bank transfer using the details above</li>
      <li>Upload your payment proof (receipt/screenshot) via the RMS portal</li>
      <li>Our admin team will verify your payment within 24 hours</li>
      <li>Your subscription will be activated immediately after verification</li>
    </ol>

    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{uploadProofUrl}}" style="background: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold;">
        Upload Payment Proof
      </a>
    </p>

    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
      If you have any questions, contact us at support@originfoodhouse.com
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
    &copy; {{year}} Origin Food House. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</body>
</html>
